{"word":"διαμαρτύρομαι","slug":"διαμαρτύρομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διαμαρτύρομαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to protest solemnly</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>obtestari</el>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a>;</b> <el>δ. μή . .</el> , <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>:— <el>δ. τινι μὴ ποιεῖν</el> <i>to protest</i> against his doing, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>generally, <i>to protest, asseverate</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to beg earnestly, conjure</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}